data.description: Step into this stunning ranch nestled in tranquil Lake Forest. As you enter, warm lvp greets your feet, inviting you into a space where comfort & style harmonize effortlessly. A cozy den/ofc space beckons. Continue into the expansive Great Room, where the gas log fireplace adds ambiance. Your eyes are drawn to the chef's kitchen, adorned with all-new upgraded Samsung SS appliances; Quartz countertops & chic backsplash elevate the space, making meal prep a joyous affair. Retreat to the large owner's suite, where custom Closets By Design offer both functionality & elegance. Immaculate & move-in ready, it promises unparalleled comfort & convenience. Experience the epitome of luxury living in this Rare Find--a sanctuary where every detail has been meticulously crafted to elevate your everyday!
